The paper deals with the joint design of content delivery and storage, which is a topic that falls under the information theory (cs.IT) and networking and internet architecture (cs.NI) sub-categories. The use of caching and coded caching is also relevant to the systems and control (cs.SI) sub-category. The paper also involves the use of entropy inequalities, which is a topic in the data structures and algorithms (cs.DS) sub-category. Finally, the paper involves optimization and performance analysis, which is a topic in the machine learning (cs.LG) sub-category.
